<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>가게 상세 정보</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/detail.css" />
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- 헤더 -->
    <div id="head">
      <div id="bookMark">
        <a href="/">
          <img src="/images/bookWhite.png" alt="북마크 아이콘" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div id="headerName">CHOI'S FoodHub</div>
      <form action="/search" method="GET">
        <div id="search">
          <input
            type="text"
            name="name"
            placeholder="식당명 입력"
            id="restaurantName"
          />
          <img
            src="/images/icon_search.png"
            alt="검색 아이콘"
            id="searchIcon"
          />
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>

    <!--  가게 상세 정보 -->
    <div class="store-container">
      <% food.forEach((x) => { %>
      <div class="left">
        <div class="image-section">
          <div class="sub-images">
            <img src="<%= x.subImage1 %>" alt="서브1 이미지" />
            <img src="<%= x.subImage2 %>" alt="서브2 이미지" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-section">
          <h2 class="resName"><%= x.resName %></h2>

          <div>⭐ <strong><%= x.rating %> / 5</strong></div>

          <div class="menu">
            <img src="/images/money.png" alt="가격 아이콘" />
            <%= x.foodName %> (<%= x.price %>원)
          </div>
          <div class="review">
            <img src="/images/review.png" alt="리뷰 아이콘" />
            <%= x.comment %>
          </div>
          <div class="address">
            <img src="/images/position.png" alt="위치 아이콘" />
            <%= x.address %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="right">
        <div class="position">
          <div id="map" style="width: 100%; height: 200px"></div>
          <span id="latitude" hidden><%= x.latitude %></span>
          <span id="longitude" hidden><%= x.longitude %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="searchInfo">
          <div class="ment1">새로운 맛집을 찾아보세요!</div>
          <div class="ment2">🍽️오늘의 맛은 여기에서 시작!</div>
          <div class="searchItems">
            <% foodList.forEach((x) => { %> <% if (x.id !== food[0].id) { %>
            <div class="searchItem">
              <a href="/detail/<%= x.id %>"> <%= x.resName %> </a>
              <img
                src="/images/icon_search.png"
                alt="위치 아이콘"
                class="searchIcon"
              />
            </div>
            <% } %> <% }) %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% }) %>
    </div>

    <!-- 푸터 -->
    <div class="bottom">
      <div class="footer-logo">
        <div class="cinemaNameBottom">CHOI'S FoodHub</div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-info">
        <p>서울특별시 송파구 올림픽로 1234 CHOI빌딩 18F</p>
        <p>
          대표 이메일: dreamcometrue@choifoodhub.co.kr | 고객센터: 1544-6848
          (유료) | 사업자등록번호: 010-00-00000
        </p>
        <p>
          대표이사: 최유진 | 개인정보 보호 책임자: 김동동 | 호스팅 제공자: CHOI
          이노베이트
        </p>
      </div>
      <p class="footer-copyright">
        Copyright © CHOI FoodHub All Rights Reserved.
      </p>
    </div>

    <script src="/static/js/detail.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
